Source: check-deleted-libs
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Simon Deziel <simon@sdeziel.info>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9)
Standards-Version: 3.9.4
Homepage: https://github.com/simondeziel/check-deleted-libs
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/simondeziel/check-deleted-libs.git

Package: check-deleted-libs
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Check processes using deleted libs/binaries
 Report processes using deleted libraries or binaries. This
 can be useful to identify which services/binaries should be
 restarted after a security patch for example.
 .
 Also supports reporting the name of VMs running outdated QEMU.
